title._content: Birdseye View of San Antonio. East of City Hall.

description._content: Title: Birdseye View of San Antonio. East of City Hall. Creator: Mary E. Jacobson Date: ca. 1892 Part Of: Album of views of Arizona, New Mexico and the southwest, 1892 Place: San Antonio, Bexar County, Texas Description: This photograph is part of an album containing photographs of Arizona and New Mexico by William Henry Jackson, as well as photographs of San Antonio, Texas, by Mary E. Jacobson. View includes signs for Cameron's, L. Wolf's, John K. Beretta & Co., and Silver King. Physical Description: 1 photographic print: albumen; 11 x 18 cm. on 27 x 34 cm. mount File: vault_ag1982_0122x_22a_sm_opt.jpg Rights: Please cite Southern Methodist University, Central University Libraries, DeGolyer Library when using this image file.
